    • Method Detail

      • showDialog

        void showDialog(java.lang.String dialogTitle,
                MetaDataContainer configData)
        Shows a dialog box with a given title and initialized with default values. The user's input is used to change values in the configuration data for the generic process.
        Parameters:
        dialogTitle - Title of the dialog box.
        configData - Data configuration for structure, input and output values of the dialog.
